      decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Browser tab animation","date":"October 23, 2024","description":"Currently I am developing the 3d portfolio, and to add accent, I wanted to add an animation at browser tab. This is a note how to add animation, with fabulous and funny."}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/3d-html-shift-problem/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Found a problem of shift the iframe or img tag in html component of drei."}},"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"877e4b8a-35a6-5c31-87fa-42dfca3084d5","previousPostId":"41f2fcbb-26fa-557e-a0f4-c3149f0bbb34","nextPostId":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383"],"slicesMap":{}}